  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Urgent Action to curb COVID to people and gorillas</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Uganda is in the midst of a severe COVID-19 surge. At Bwindi, limited awareness and poor access to health care leave people and the endangered mountain gorillas at massive risk. The effects of COVID-19 transmission from people to the closely related endangered mountain gorillas would be catastrophic for the species. We must protect the people and gorillas of Bwindi by urgently establishing 57 Village COVID-19 Taskforces to support home-based care, community surveillance and prevention awareness.</narrative>
  </description>
